<br>

<div class="row justify-content-center text-white text-special">
    <h2 class="text-white m-2">Welcome To Pickem Dota 2</h2>
</div>
<div class="row justify-content-center text-white text-special">
    <p class="text-white m-2">Predict Major Dota League Games to Win Prizes!</p>
</div>

<div class="container mt-2 mb-2">
    <div class="row">
            <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" style="width: 100%; height: 30rem;">
                <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                    <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                    <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                    <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
                </ol>
                <div class="carousel-inner" style="width: 100%;">
                    <div class="carousel-item p-2 active">
                        <div class="row justify-content-center text-special">
                            <h2 class="d-block mx-auto text-white">Upcoming Tournament</h2>
                        </div>
                        <%= image_tag("brand/upcoming.png", class: "d-block mx-auto", style: "width:50%;") %>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item p-2">
                        <div class="row justify-content-center text-special">
                            <h2 class="text-white">Prize Allocation</h2>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row justify-content-center text-special p-4">
                            <ul>
                                <li>First Prize: RM 5500</li>
                                <li>Second Prize: RM 2500</li>
                                <li>Third Prize: RM 1250</li>
                                <li>Forth Prize: RM 750</li>
                                <li>Fifth Prize: RM 500</li>
                                <li>Sixth Prize: RM 500</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item p-2">
                        <div class="row justify-content-center text-special">
                            <h2 class="text-white">How To Participate?</h2>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row justify-content-center text-white text-small">
                            <ul>
                                <li>
                                    <span class="badge badge-info">Step 1 </span> Signed Up for Pickemd2 and completed verification process.
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <span class="badge badge-info">Step 2</span> Predict 5 questions per match for all matches in the published Tournament.
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <span class="badge badge-info">Step 3</span> Each correct prediction earn 1 point and player accumulated most point throughout the Tournament will win the prize!
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <span class="badge badge-info">Step 4</span> Player must complete all predictions 60 minutes prior to official per match time to avoid any complications.
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <span class="badge badge-info">Step 5</span> Once the tournament is ended and when the top scorers are finalized, our Admin will contact winner for awarding the prize within 3days!
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <span class="badge badge-info">Step 6</span> Please do not hesitate to contact via whatsapp to admin contact or email to us.
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                </a>
                <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
                    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                </a>
            </div>
    </div>
</div>

<br><br>